{
  "stem": "293.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I finished high--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, you know, let me tell you something about my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't have a university degree, but he has a high school degree.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was extremely talented, spoke fluently few languages; Polish, German, English, Hebrew, Yiddish, and in writing and speaking.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he wrote beautifully.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was very talented in writing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't have the talents of my--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was one of the lucky one who had went to the government high school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This meant free of paying, free of charge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to the high school in city of Podgorze, very prominent high school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's not like here, high school here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Gymnasium was a much, much higher level because the classes-- when I was-- I was 10 years old when I went to the first class of gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have already three",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German, Latin, and Greek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Coincidentally, it was substantial amount.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the class was roughly between 35 and 40 students, was about 50% was a Jewish student.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have no problem in the-- in the high school with anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, again, the Jews and things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only problem was",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "to get to the gymnasium, you have to be at B plus student minimum.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When, for example, general public, the Catholic student could get the minute they are entitled to go, they were accepted.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have to come- go-- everybody has to go through the entry examination, but was much more difficult to pass for the Jewish boy, the demand was much bigger, because they have to eliminate it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "According of the status of Poland-- because in Poland, an average was between 3 and a-- 3 and a half million Jewish population before the-- between first and second war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They quotas.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
